Status: `VERIFIED` Step-4 friendly maxima with `INFERRED` repair sheet

On the frozen Step-4 ledger, the largest recorded friendly leakage loads
across `F_SS(1/12)` and `F_SL(1/16)` are:
`L_tot = 1/4`,
`L_mirror = 1/12`,
